Package pt.ist.fenixframework.backend

Interface Summary
BackEnd Each concrete back end should implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
BackEndId This class represents a feature that all DML code generators must implement: All CodeGenerator implementations should generate a class named CurrentBackEndId (see CodeGenerator.generateBackEndId()) that implements this abstract class and provides information about the current backend that is being used to manage the domain model.
